1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,980
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 22 =

20
00:01:37,020 --> 00:01:37,860
Come and have a look.

21
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:39,460
You won’t be disappointed.

22
00:01:44,180 --> 00:01:46,220
Excuse me. How much is this?

23
00:01:46,234 --> 00:01:48,389
A pot of liquor, please.

24
00:01:56,597 --> 00:01:58,042
All on sale!

25
00:02:04,500 --> 00:02:06,700
Meat buns are 14 coppers each.

26
00:02:07,180 --> 00:02:09,460
Lamb offal and chicken skin buns, 12 each.

27
00:02:09,740 --> 00:02:10,860
Vegetable ones, 10 each.

28
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:12,660
The price is low.

29
00:02:20,380 --> 00:02:21,540
I thought colored clay dolls

30
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:23,060
could only be seen in the south.

31
00:02:28,980 --> 00:02:30,700
There are meat-stuffed desserts from Suzhou, too.

32
00:02:31,780 --> 00:02:33,380
I wonder how well they taste.

33
00:02:33,740 --> 00:02:34,580
Stop the carriage.

34
00:02:49,980 --> 00:02:51,020
Taste it.

35
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:06,580
This is it.

36
00:03:10,820 --> 00:03:12,020
It’s said in the poem,

37
00:03:12,780 --> 00:03:15,820
“Transportation of goods relies on merchants.

38
00:03:16,060 --> 00:03:19,740
People near and far gather at noon to trade”.

39
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:22,100
Merchants travel all over the country,

40
00:03:22,100 --> 00:03:23,500
moving surpluses of one area

41
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:25,180
to places that are short of them.

42
00:03:25,700 --> 00:03:27,740
Their hard work benefits the state and themselves.

43
00:03:29,780 --> 00:03:30,740
It’s my poem.

44
00:03:31,740 --> 00:03:32,860
When I wrote it

45
00:03:32,860 --> 00:03:34,140
a few years back,

46
00:03:34,820 --> 00:03:36,820
I intended to express my wish

47
00:03:36,900 --> 00:03:38,220
and plan in my head.

48
00:03:38,580 --> 00:03:39,780
It’s only been over a decade,

49
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:40,660
yet Kaifeng

50
00:03:41,020 --> 00:03:43,100
has become so prosperous.

51
00:03:57,660 --> 00:04:00,260
Isn’t it time to close the market?

52
00:04:00,740 --> 00:04:02,700
How come the street is more crowded?

53
00:04:05,780 --> 00:04:07,100
You probably don’t know

54
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:09,660
that Your Majesty’s decree last spring

55
00:04:09,940 --> 00:04:12,820
canceled rings for market opening and closing here.

56
00:04:14,060 --> 00:04:14,900
In Kaifeng,

57
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:16,980
there are no time limits for trading.

58
00:04:17,260 --> 00:04:18,700
Commoners can sell

59
00:04:18,700 --> 00:04:20,620
their homemade food and clothes

60
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:21,900
as long as their stalls

61
00:04:21,900 --> 00:04:23,500
don’t outstretch the curb.

62
00:04:55,660 --> 00:04:57,580
People can trade at any time and place.

63
00:04:57,900 --> 00:04:58,980
It’s much more convenient.

64
00:04:59,620 --> 00:05:01,100
No wonder I could hardly recognize this city

65
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,660
after being away for three years.

66
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:05,260
It’s booming.

67
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:15,380
This book is printed from

68
00:05:15,460 --> 00:05:17,740
Cai Junmo’s poems Four Sages and a Fool.

69
00:05:17,860 --> 00:05:19,020
Skilled craftsmen

70
00:05:19,340 --> 00:05:20,340
modeled it

71
00:05:20,340 --> 00:05:21,500
on Cai Junmo’s handwriting version.

72
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:23,980
Clay characters were assembled for printing.

73
00:05:24,380 --> 00:05:27,500
= Four Sages and a Fool =
The ink is the finest and the pages are glued together.

74
00:05:27,940 --> 00:05:29,820
“After appointed as censor,

75
00:05:29,860 --> 00:05:31,940
his talents revealed.

76
00:05:32,100 --> 00:05:33,780
Criticisms didn’t break him

77
00:05:33,780 --> 00:05:35,620
but only refined him”.

78
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:38,060
The first out of the Four Sages

79
00:05:38,140 --> 00:05:39,100
refers to Fan Zhongyan

80
00:05:39,220 --> 00:05:41,580
who impeached Prime Minister with his painting

81
00:05:41,700 --> 00:05:43,500
and insisted that he’d never bend to power.

82
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:44,860
He’d rather die to be heard

83
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:47,780
than live in silence.

84
00:05:48,500 --> 00:05:49,620
Have a look.

85
00:05:49,620 --> 00:05:50,420
Take a look.

86
00:05:50,420 --> 00:05:51,820
Wasn’t His Majesty wrong that he was misled

87
00:05:52,380 --> 00:05:54,700
by a rat and demoted a loyal official?

88
00:05:57,860 --> 00:06:00,000
His Majesty is too busy

89
00:06:00,780 --> 00:06:01,780
- Prime Minister Lv once criticized me.
- to attend to everything himself.

90
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:04,660
He claimed that I always made dangerous remarks.

91
00:06:05,060 --> 00:06:07,300
- to gain fame and I was impractical.
- Who was that rat?

92
00:06:07,317 --> 00:06:09,220
Censor Gao is the Fool in the title.

93
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:10,060
I know

94
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:12,220
you never hunger for fame,

95
00:06:13,660 --> 00:06:14,740
but I wonder

96
00:06:15,740 --> 00:06:17,100
how certain you are

97
00:06:17,460 --> 00:06:18,940
that all your harsh criticisms

98
00:06:18,980 --> 00:06:20,180
of my faults,

99
00:06:20,180 --> 00:06:21,700
complaints about ministers

100
00:06:21,740 --> 00:06:24,460
are factual, fair and unbiased.

101
00:06:41,700 --> 00:06:42,420
Your Majesty,

102
00:06:47,620 --> 00:06:50,140
I meant everything I voiced.

103
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:52,340
There were no selfish motives.

104
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:54,420
But my knowledge is limited

105
00:06:54,780 --> 00:06:56,500
and I can only see so much,

106
00:06:56,860 --> 00:06:59,180
so I’m not sure

107
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:01,540
if my opinions are completely fair.

108
00:07:03,060 --> 00:07:04,660
Were all officials like you

109
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:07,060
being completely honest with me,

110
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:10,740
I’d be able to see the whole picture.

111
00:07:17,460 --> 00:07:18,460
Even with that in hand,

112
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:21,100
one might not be able to grab the gist

113
00:07:21,620 --> 00:07:23,060
and come up with perfect strategies.

114
00:07:25,260 --> 00:07:26,900
Nothing is perfect.

115
00:07:27,580 --> 00:07:29,100
We can only do our best.

116
00:07:32,020 --> 00:07:32,420
Your Majesty,

117
00:07:33,380 --> 00:07:34,540
the gate is about to be closed.

118
00:07:34,540 --> 00:07:36,300
We should head back to the palace.

119
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:41,420
Have someone talk to the bookstall owner.

120
00:07:41,500 --> 00:07:42,580
Characters in his books

121
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:44,940
are almost identical to Cai Junmo’s handwriting.

122
00:07:45,220 --> 00:07:46,820
Ask him where he found

123
00:07:47,060 --> 00:07:49,060
such engravers skilled at calligraphy.

124
00:07:49,260 --> 00:07:50,540
Some books in our library

125
00:07:50,540 --> 00:07:52,020
can’t be found elsewhere.

126
00:07:52,580 --> 00:07:53,740
More copies should be made

127
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:56,500
for Directorate of Education and Academies

128
00:07:56,820 --> 00:07:58,420
to broaden students’ horizons.

129
00:07:59,780 --> 00:08:00,540
Yes.

130
00:08:06,940 --> 00:08:09,780
People in Kaifeng no longer need

131
00:08:10,220 --> 00:08:12,780
to follow a strict timetable

132
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:14,900
or separate business and living quarters,

133
00:08:16,380 --> 00:08:17,380
but I...

134
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:37,020
Tomorrow...

135
00:08:44,340 --> 00:08:47,140
Your Majesty, once I arrive in the west,

136
00:08:47,380 --> 00:08:48,340
if enemies dare to invade,

137
00:08:48,660 --> 00:08:50,020
no one can cross the border

138
00:08:50,180 --> 00:08:51,540
without walking over me first.

139
00:08:52,020 --> 00:08:52,860
If the border is at peace,

140
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,100
I’ll do my utmost to serve the locals,

141
00:08:55,340 --> 00:08:57,660
enrich them and educate them

142
00:08:58,060 --> 00:08:59,260
in order to establish new trends and customs

143
00:08:59,580 --> 00:09:02,300
and build a richer and safer region

144
00:09:03,060 --> 00:09:04,060
for the sake of the future.

145
00:09:06,020 --> 00:09:07,500
I hope one day,

146
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:09,540
your ambition will come true.

147
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:14,620
On our way to the west,

148
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,700
we’ll remember today’s remarks.

149
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:18,940
On the battlefield, we won’t forget

150
00:09:19,380 --> 00:09:22,340
behind us is our flourishing capital.

151
00:09:26,060 --> 00:09:26,940
Thank you

152
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:32,580
for your services.

153
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:54,620
I could only watch from the carriage outside.

154
00:09:55,060 --> 00:09:55,900
It was suffocating.

155
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:58,660
Here I can finally get out and walk.

156
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:01,580
You may all leave

157
00:10:01,860 --> 00:10:03,460
except for Maoze.

158
00:10:12,260 --> 00:10:14,060
You’re finally back, Your Majesty.

159
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:16,220
Empress has been waiting for you since noon.

160
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:18,300
Madam Zhang seems

161
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:20,700
to be possessed by some nightmare

162
00:10:21,140 --> 00:10:22,500
and keeps saying that I,

163
00:10:22,580 --> 00:10:23,980
Imperial Physicians and everyone around her

164
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:25,020
are trying to harm her baby.

165
00:10:26,900 --> 00:10:28,220
Luckily, Empress is there

166
00:10:28,660 --> 00:10:29,820
the whole time.

167
00:10:30,220 --> 00:10:32,100
She hasn’t had any rest.

168
00:10:34,620 --> 00:10:35,620
His Majesty has arrived.

169
00:10:43,860 --> 00:10:44,500
Danshu.

170
00:10:44,540 --> 00:10:45,260
Your Majesty.

171
00:10:45,380 --> 00:10:47,500
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

172
00:10:47,620 --> 00:10:48,140
Bihan.

173
00:10:48,140 --> 00:10:48,980
Your Majesty!

174
00:10:48,980 --> 00:10:49,660
Bihan.

175
00:10:51,540 --> 00:10:52,300
Bihan.

176
00:10:55,300 --> 00:10:56,700
There, there. I’m here.

177
00:10:57,100 --> 00:10:57,740
You’re safe.

178
00:10:57,740 --> 00:10:58,740
Your Majesty!

179
00:10:59,700 --> 00:11:00,620
Alright. There, there.

180
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:05,460
Your Majesty.

181
00:11:08,060 --> 00:11:09,580
I couldn’t pacify Madam Zhang

182
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:11,300
at her chamber.

183
00:11:12,180 --> 00:11:14,180
Given that she’s pregnant,

184
00:11:14,660 --> 00:11:16,300
I took the liberty

185
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:18,460
to have her escorted to your residence.

186
00:11:21,980 --> 00:11:24,540
You can punish me tomorrow

187
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,860
for my mistake.

188
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:31,340
Alright. Calm down.

189
00:11:40,380 --> 00:11:41,340
Your Majesty.

190
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,820
Don’t cry.

191
00:12:23,780 --> 00:12:25,020
His Majesty loves me.

192
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:28,020
Why would I compete against others?

193
00:12:29,220 --> 00:12:31,220
Among a dozen consorts superior to me,

194
00:12:31,340 --> 00:12:32,700
how many of them His Majesty truly loves

195
00:12:32,700 --> 00:12:33,980
instead of being forced to marry?

196
00:13:33,860 --> 00:13:34,580
Your Highness.

197
00:13:39,620 --> 00:13:40,340
Your Highness.

198
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:43,020
I’ll study and work hard.

199
00:13:44,020 --> 00:13:46,460
I’ll take good care of you

200
00:13:47,540 --> 00:13:49,140
= Zhao Zongshi =
and imprison everyone

201
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:50,580
that upsets you.

202
00:13:57,660 --> 00:13:58,460
Zongshi,

203
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:02,100
do you remember

204
00:14:02,100 --> 00:14:03,460
I once told you

205
00:14:04,060 --> 00:14:05,820
to be sincere yet restrained?

206
00:14:07,420 --> 00:14:08,380
Your Highness.

207
00:14:17,980 --> 00:14:19,620
I didn’t mean to blame you.

208
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:24,660
I...

209
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:28,620
I want to study classics

210
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:33,380
with you

211
00:14:34,460 --> 00:14:36,820
to control my excessive anger, hatred

212
00:14:40,780 --> 00:14:42,580
and affection.

213
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:47,460
It’s true that someone is trying to harm me.

214
00:14:48,300 --> 00:14:49,620
Do you remember

215
00:14:50,020 --> 00:14:51,540
someone once set me up

216
00:14:52,020 --> 00:14:53,780
and locked me in the woodshed?

217
00:14:53,780 --> 00:14:55,180
I almost got wronged

218
00:14:55,180 --> 00:14:56,100
and kicked out of the palace

219
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:57,500
and separated from you forever.

220
00:14:58,140 --> 00:14:59,540
The past is the past.

221
00:14:59,940 --> 00:15:01,740
Didn’t I protect you back then?

222
00:15:02,860 --> 00:15:03,700
I’m here with you.

223
00:15:07,300 --> 00:15:08,620
That’s why I only trust you

224
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:11,060
in this entire palace.

225
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:13,420
Only you can make me feel safe.

226
00:15:14,740 --> 00:15:15,940
But I can’t always

227
00:15:15,940 --> 00:15:16,940
be with you.

228
00:15:17,300 --> 00:15:18,700
You’re pregnant

229
00:15:18,700 --> 00:15:19,980
and need to be taken good care of.

230
00:15:22,660 --> 00:15:23,420
Your Majesty,

231
00:15:24,700 --> 00:15:26,940
can my aunt stay with me?

232
00:15:31,180 --> 00:15:32,460
You mean Instructor Jia?

233
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,340
She’s calculative,

234
00:15:38,060 --> 00:15:39,100
cunning and greedy.

235
00:15:41,300 --> 00:15:43,180
I was the victim

236
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:46,140
yet my aunt, the only protector

237
00:15:46,140 --> 00:15:47,540
was thrown out of the palace.

238
00:15:49,580 --> 00:15:50,780
That culprit

239
00:15:51,980 --> 00:15:53,660
still works at the Institute because Empress

240
00:15:53,660 --> 00:15:55,100
found no solid evidence against her.

241
00:15:57,340 --> 00:15:58,460
About that,

242
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:00,980
I trusted you

243
00:16:01,180 --> 00:16:02,620
and so did Empress,

244
00:16:04,100 --> 00:16:05,380
but the evidence was lacking.

245
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:07,060
Your speculation alone

246
00:16:07,060 --> 00:16:08,140
couldn’t convict others,

247
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:11,860
but Instructor Jia

248
00:16:11,860 --> 00:16:13,020
did violate the rules.

249
00:16:13,020 --> 00:16:15,180
Empress was lenient enough with her

250
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:16,340
considering the situation.

251
00:16:20,900 --> 00:16:22,300
Empress is

252
00:16:22,300 --> 00:16:23,700
the perfect and greatest woman in the world.

253
00:16:24,220 --> 00:16:25,660
She’s always right.

254
00:16:26,940 --> 00:16:27,900
Compared with her,

255
00:16:27,900 --> 00:16:29,580
I’m the evilest.

256
00:16:32,660 --> 00:16:33,340
Tomorrow,

257
00:16:33,820 --> 00:16:34,660
I’ll tell Shouzhong

258
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:35,620
to find someone else

259
00:16:35,620 --> 00:16:36,460
you like.

260
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:40,580
Ren Shouzhong doesn’t respect me.

261
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:43,500
No.

262
00:16:45,340 --> 00:16:46,660
He’s ill-intentioned.

263
00:16:47,860 --> 00:16:49,580
Must it be Instructor Jia?

264
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:54,260
Your Majesty, after my father died,

265
00:16:54,420 --> 00:16:55,540
my mother and I were on ourselves.

266
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,180
All these years,

267
00:16:57,180 --> 00:16:58,780
only my aunt treats me well.

268
00:17:12,460 --> 00:17:13,220
Alright.

269
00:17:21,580 --> 00:17:23,940
Your Highness, don’t be sad.

270
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:26,140
When I grow up...

271
00:17:28,060 --> 00:17:31,300
I am angry and sad,

272
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:34,780
but nobody

273
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,500
can always be happy,

274
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:37,220
right?

275
00:17:37,780 --> 00:17:38,420
Yes.

276
00:17:38,700 --> 00:17:40,340
I’m a bit upset, too.

277
00:17:47,540 --> 00:17:48,460
I know

278
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:54,540
you miss your own family

279
00:17:55,780 --> 00:17:56,780
and you want His Majesty

280
00:17:56,780 --> 00:17:58,340
to love you the same as Huirou.

281
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:02,380
I don’t want to lie

282
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:04,300
and tell you he treats you

283
00:18:04,620 --> 00:18:05,940
and Huirou the same.

284
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:09,260
What I want you to know is

285
00:18:11,100 --> 00:18:12,220
in this world,

286
00:18:13,660 --> 00:18:15,620
nobody can have everything they want

287
00:18:16,820 --> 00:18:18,620
or always be happy and loved by everyone.

288
00:18:18,780 --> 00:18:21,820
Not you, not me,

289
00:18:25,980 --> 00:18:27,380
not even His Majesty.

290
00:18:28,820 --> 00:18:31,220
We have to be strong and tolerant.

291
00:18:33,180 --> 00:18:34,420
Why can’t His Majesty?

292
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:36,660
He owns the world.

293
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,980
Everyone has to listen to him.

294
00:18:43,660 --> 00:18:44,420
Because...

295
00:18:46,780 --> 00:18:48,540
he’s the ruler of the state

296
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:51,260
who has to look after everyone.

297
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:52,220
Your Majesty.

298
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:55,860
You’re still here.

299
00:20:04,220 --> 00:20:04,980
Good.

300
00:20:06,540 --> 00:20:07,900
Go to Empress’s chamber with me.

301
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:41,900
Your Majesty.

302
00:20:41,900 --> 00:20:42,780
You must be tired, too.

303
00:20:43,860 --> 00:20:45,140
Skip the formalities.

304
00:20:46,980 --> 00:20:47,620
Have a seat.

305
00:20:48,380 --> 00:20:49,180
Serve some tea.

306
00:20:49,180 --> 00:20:49,820
Yes.

307
00:20:50,060 --> 00:20:50,820
No need.

308
00:20:51,180 --> 00:20:52,140
You may leave.

309
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:13,380
You had a long day.

310
00:21:18,700 --> 00:21:19,900
I did my best

311
00:21:21,900 --> 00:21:23,060
but failed

312
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:25,540
to handle things properly.

313
00:21:25,740 --> 00:21:27,540
It was embarrassing.

314
00:21:28,260 --> 00:21:30,420
Physicians and servants witnessed the whole scene.

315
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:39,980
It’s a long and difficult day for you.

316
00:21:41,660 --> 00:21:43,060
Bihan is unruly.

317
00:21:45,260 --> 00:21:46,620
At first, I thought

318
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:48,740
she was young.

319
00:21:49,820 --> 00:21:51,180
She was only 14 when she came,

320
00:21:51,180 --> 00:21:52,260
so I indulged her.

321
00:21:54,500 --> 00:21:55,900
She should’ve been punished

322
00:21:56,340 --> 00:21:57,660
for her wild behavior

323
00:21:57,780 --> 00:22:00,780
but her mood is unstable

324
00:22:00,980 --> 00:22:02,060
and she’s still weak.

325
00:22:05,780 --> 00:22:07,340
You have no sons for years

326
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:10,180
and only have one daughter

327
00:22:11,140 --> 00:22:12,860
who was born by my closest friend

328
00:22:12,860 --> 00:22:13,940
Madam Miao.

329
00:22:15,060 --> 00:22:18,100
So people start to doubt me.

330
00:22:20,300 --> 00:22:22,140
I’m unable to defend myself.

331
00:22:23,620 --> 00:22:25,100
Only after Madam Zhang’s baby

332
00:22:25,100 --> 00:22:26,180
arriving safely

333
00:22:27,900 --> 00:22:29,180
will I be proven innocent.

334
00:22:34,700 --> 00:22:36,300
Bihan is simply too nervous.

335
00:22:38,060 --> 00:22:39,100
But I assure you

336
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:42,060
nobody here and outside, including me,

337
00:22:42,660 --> 00:22:44,620
doubts your nobility.

338
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:51,100
Your words

339
00:22:52,100 --> 00:22:53,860
do make me feel a bit relieved.

340
00:22:57,900 --> 00:22:58,820
Your Majesty,

341
00:23:01,340 --> 00:23:02,140
I have

342
00:23:03,660 --> 00:23:05,300
a request.

343
00:23:07,300 --> 00:23:07,980
What is it?

344
00:23:10,580 --> 00:23:12,140
Recalling Instructor Jia to the palace

345
00:23:12,660 --> 00:23:14,140
to look after Madam Zhang during her pregnancy

346
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:24,820
is against the rules

347
00:23:26,580 --> 00:23:28,420
and she isn’t decent,

348
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:31,020
but I’m unable

349
00:23:31,020 --> 00:23:32,740
to gain Madam Zhang’s trust.

350
00:23:34,980 --> 00:23:36,460
Without people she trusts

351
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:37,540
by her side,

352
00:23:38,380 --> 00:23:39,380
today’s incident

353
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:41,500
is going to repeat itself.

354
00:23:42,180 --> 00:23:43,100
Then how should I

355
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:44,940
discipline other concubines,

356
00:23:44,940 --> 00:23:45,900
servants and maids?

357
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:49,700
After careful consideration,

358
00:23:50,180 --> 00:23:51,620
we should make everyone realize

359
00:23:53,100 --> 00:23:55,460
that Madam Zhang is Your Majesty’s favorite

360
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:56,740
in the entire harem.

361
00:23:57,380 --> 00:23:58,460
I dare not rule over her.

362
00:23:58,780 --> 00:24:00,300
Only Your Majesty has such rights.

363
00:24:09,580 --> 00:24:10,380
Danshu,

364
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,980
you have every right

365
00:24:14,220 --> 00:24:15,180
to be mad at me.

366
00:24:16,660 --> 00:24:18,140
Once she gets better,

367
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:20,380
I’ll talk to her.

368
00:24:22,700 --> 00:24:24,380
I’m not mad at you.

369
00:24:27,380 --> 00:24:28,620
You know it yourself

370
00:24:29,620 --> 00:24:30,020
that Madam Zhang

371
00:24:30,020 --> 00:24:31,620
will never trust me

372
00:24:33,060 --> 00:24:34,780
unless I can punish her

373
00:24:34,980 --> 00:24:35,900
without considering her health

374
00:24:36,020 --> 00:24:37,180
or her baby’s.

375
00:24:37,740 --> 00:24:39,420
Then she might be afraid of me.

376
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:44,100
But I can’t bear such consequences.

377
00:24:48,100 --> 00:24:49,820
All I want to say is,

378
00:24:51,580 --> 00:24:52,660
from now on,

379
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:54,900
you can indulge

380
00:24:54,900 --> 00:24:56,300
or discipline her as you wish.

381
00:24:58,180 --> 00:24:59,820
As long as she doesn’t break the laws,

382
00:25:00,140 --> 00:25:01,340
I’ll turn a blind eye

383
00:25:01,620 --> 00:25:02,580
to her other behaviors.

384
00:25:04,060 --> 00:25:05,180
If she does violate the laws,

385
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:09,100
you won’t tolerate her

386
00:25:09,900 --> 00:25:11,460
and will surely punish her.

387
00:25:29,620 --> 00:25:30,300
It’s late.

388
00:25:31,980 --> 00:25:33,900
You look exhausted.

389
00:25:37,020 --> 00:25:39,820
Please go back and rest.

390
00:26:01,300 --> 00:26:02,780
Your Majesty...

391
00:26:02,860 --> 00:26:04,060
I don’t want to go back!

392
00:26:10,700 --> 00:26:12,820
Your Majesty! Your Majesty!

393
00:26:35,980 --> 00:26:36,820
I’m fine.

394
00:26:48,380 --> 00:26:49,260
Hey,

395
00:26:50,740 --> 00:26:52,540
did you have something to report

396
00:26:53,860 --> 00:26:55,340
so you waited outside my chamber?

397
00:26:57,060 --> 00:26:57,900
What is it?

398
00:26:58,460 --> 00:27:01,540
Your Majesty, the ground is cold.

399
00:27:02,260 --> 00:27:03,460
Let me carry you.

400
00:27:07,900 --> 00:27:09,580
I don’t know where I can go.

401
00:27:12,060 --> 00:27:14,260
The empress didn't want me to stay

402
00:27:15,860 --> 00:27:17,940
and I don’t want to go back to my own chamber.

403
00:27:22,500 --> 00:27:24,660
I was mad at Bihan

404
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,620
but seeing her like that,

405
00:27:29,420 --> 00:27:30,420
it pained me,

406
00:27:32,380 --> 00:27:33,740
so I couldn’t reprimand her.

407
00:27:34,460 --> 00:27:38,940
Let me carry you to Madam Miao’s place.

408
00:27:45,940 --> 00:27:47,180
Xinhe and Huirou

409
00:27:49,260 --> 00:27:52,300
must’ve heard the noise, too.

410
00:27:53,860 --> 00:27:55,180
They’d blame me, too.

411
00:27:55,780 --> 00:27:57,380
Princess is only two years old.

412
00:28:03,700 --> 00:28:06,060
It’s not too cold today.

413
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:08,500
The air outside is fresher.

414
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:11,060
Let me carry you to help you relax.

415
00:28:11,540 --> 00:28:12,740
You can say anything to me.

416
00:28:17,540 --> 00:28:19,740
By replacing that geezer Fan Yong

417
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:22,420
with Fan Zhongyan and Han Qi,

418
00:28:23,580 --> 00:28:25,540
I hope the situation in the west can pick up.

419
00:28:30,020 --> 00:28:31,700
Did Fan Yong underestimated the enemies,

420
00:28:32,380 --> 00:28:34,580
leading to our failure at Sanchuankou?

421
00:28:35,580 --> 00:28:37,220
Are there officials, once deployed,

422
00:28:37,220 --> 00:28:39,020
who can turn the table

423
00:28:39,020 --> 00:28:40,100
and gain the ultimate victory?

424
00:28:42,540 --> 00:28:43,500
I don’t think so.

425
00:28:48,260 --> 00:28:49,620
When I was little,

426
00:28:49,940 --> 00:28:52,340
I pictured how to be a good emperor

427
00:28:54,100 --> 00:28:55,980
and secretly wished to outdo my predecessors

428
00:28:56,380 --> 00:28:58,100
and expand the territory.

429
00:28:58,460 --> 00:29:01,140
I’d follow in other great emperors’ steps.

430
00:29:03,380 --> 00:29:04,180
Later,

431
00:29:05,940 --> 00:29:07,620
when the Empress Dowager was in charge,

432
00:29:09,020 --> 00:29:10,300
I couldn’t wait to rule the state independently.

433
00:29:11,820 --> 00:29:13,500
Then when her death

434
00:29:13,980 --> 00:29:15,100
shook the court,

435
00:29:16,180 --> 00:29:17,980
I had to stabilize the situation.

436
00:29:20,060 --> 00:29:21,060
After that,

437
00:29:23,780 --> 00:29:24,900
I realized

438
00:29:25,940 --> 00:29:27,980
how good the old days were

439
00:29:28,180 --> 00:29:29,580
when I had so many wishes.

440
00:29:31,660 --> 00:29:33,740
Right now, my biggest fear

441
00:29:34,420 --> 00:29:37,300
is disappointing the state and the people.

442
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:45,580
I feel better.

443
00:29:45,940 --> 00:29:47,180
Put me down.

444
00:29:59,140 --> 00:30:00,020
Maoze,

445
00:30:01,100 --> 00:30:03,140
you waited outside for so long

446
00:30:03,140 --> 00:30:04,340
to report something to me, didn’t you?

447
00:30:05,940 --> 00:30:08,060
Have you found leads related to Liu Ping’s case?

448
00:30:17,020 --> 00:30:19,260
There’s more to Liu Ping’s case.

449
00:30:19,900 --> 00:30:21,540
A thorough investigation is needed.

450
00:30:22,540 --> 00:30:24,220
When I was at the Privy Council,

451
00:30:25,180 --> 00:30:28,140
I read all the military reports

452
00:30:28,340 --> 00:30:29,700
from Qing County, Huan County and Yan’an.

453
00:30:31,180 --> 00:30:32,500
There were witnesses

454
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:33,700
but I lost them.

455
00:30:34,820 --> 00:30:36,260
I saw that Censor Han and Scholar Fu

456
00:30:36,260 --> 00:30:37,860
also found those two injured soldiers

457
00:30:38,380 --> 00:30:39,140
and had guards escort them

458
00:30:39,140 --> 00:30:40,860
to testify at Hezhong Municipal Government

459
00:30:41,100 --> 00:30:42,220
in a low profile.

460
00:30:42,900 --> 00:30:44,700
I also had men

461
00:30:44,940 --> 00:30:46,300
monitor Huang Dehe’s guards and family

462
00:30:46,420 --> 00:30:47,460
in the Capital.

463
00:30:49,220 --> 00:30:50,260
You lost the witnesses?

464
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:52,500
They were killed

465
00:30:53,100 --> 00:30:54,620
and made to look like a robbery gone wrong?

466
00:30:55,180 --> 00:30:57,380
You didn’t find out who did it?

467
00:31:00,980 --> 00:31:03,500
I’m guilty. Please punish me.

468
00:31:14,100 --> 00:31:15,700
Punish me, Your Majesty.

469
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:17,540
Don’t punish yourself.

470
00:31:19,060 --> 00:31:20,820
Punish you?

471
00:31:23,900 --> 00:31:25,340
Ministries were inefficient.

472
00:31:25,340 --> 00:31:27,460
Wang Sui asked me to punish him.

473
00:31:27,940 --> 00:31:30,220
So did Fan Yong after losing the battle.

474
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:31,860
Followed by Wen Yanbo,

475
00:31:31,860 --> 00:31:32,860
when he couldn’t solve Liu Ping’s case.

476
00:31:32,860 --> 00:31:34,220
Then there was Danshu asking for punishment

477
00:31:34,220 --> 00:31:35,500
for being unable to discipline Bihan.

478
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:36,580
And you too

479
00:31:36,580 --> 00:31:37,620
after losing the witnesses.

480
00:31:38,460 --> 00:31:39,980
You all asked me to punish you.

481
00:31:40,620 --> 00:31:43,100
I might as well kneel at the ancestral hall

482
00:31:43,100 --> 00:31:44,380
and confess to heaven and ancestors

483
00:31:44,460 --> 00:31:46,260
that I’m incompetent. Please punish me.

484
00:31:55,180 --> 00:31:56,580
After the witnesses were killed,

485
00:31:57,300 --> 00:31:58,980
I continued the investigation in secret.

486
00:32:03,140 --> 00:32:05,220
Did someone at Kaifeng Municipal Government

487
00:32:05,700 --> 00:32:07,180
or Ministry of Justice collude with Huang Dehe?

488
00:32:09,300 --> 00:32:10,660
Are there other witnesses

489
00:32:11,220 --> 00:32:12,780
other than the deceased?

490
00:32:15,700 --> 00:32:16,460
Yes.

491
00:32:17,140 --> 00:32:18,700
Liu Ping’s son, Liu Yisun

492
00:32:18,820 --> 00:32:20,060
survived the assassination.

493
00:32:20,300 --> 00:32:21,780
He should be in Hezhong

494
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:22,820
or the Capital.

495
00:32:23,100 --> 00:32:24,420
General Lu Zheng

496
00:32:24,420 --> 00:32:26,020
also escaped from Yuanhao’s hands.

497
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:28,140
20 guards of the Imperial Security Agency

498
00:32:28,340 --> 00:32:29,620
were dispatched to look for him in the west.

499
00:32:30,380 --> 00:32:31,140
Well...

500
00:32:31,780 --> 00:32:32,780
I thought

501
00:32:33,140 --> 00:32:34,820
the Imperial Security Agency was different

502
00:32:34,820 --> 00:32:36,380
from the municipal government or other ministries.

503
00:32:36,860 --> 00:32:38,740
Your Majesty only needed to know the leads.

504
00:32:39,380 --> 00:32:40,260
It was

505
00:32:41,100 --> 00:32:42,580
up to Censor Wen, Scholar Fu and the others

506
00:32:42,780 --> 00:32:44,260
to follow them to investigate.

507
00:32:44,780 --> 00:32:45,780
That was the routine.

508
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:48,780
I already figured out

509
00:32:49,380 --> 00:32:50,660
the truth of Liu Ping’s case,

510
00:32:51,860 --> 00:32:53,140
but I want Huang Dehe

511
00:32:53,140 --> 00:32:54,500
to be brought to justice

512
00:32:54,860 --> 00:32:56,900
in front of everyone without doubts.

513
00:32:59,260 --> 00:32:59,900
It’s strange

514
00:33:01,660 --> 00:33:02,860
that he was low-ranking and far from the Capital

515
00:33:03,740 --> 00:33:05,420
but knew everything happened here.

516
00:33:06,100 --> 00:33:07,700
Witnesses were killed right after they were found.

517
00:33:08,980 --> 00:33:11,500
And he could anticipate government operations.

518
00:33:13,020 --> 00:33:13,980
Were there secret dealings involved?

519
00:33:14,820 --> 00:33:16,540
Generals at the border could smuggle salt

520
00:33:16,860 --> 00:33:17,820
and they had connections

521
00:33:17,820 --> 00:33:19,380
to sell girls here to those at the border.

522
00:33:19,740 --> 00:33:20,700
They were in cahoots.

523
00:33:22,660 --> 00:33:23,380
Dig deeper.

524
00:33:24,300 --> 00:33:26,180
Mobilize the entire Imperial Security Agency.

525
00:33:27,980 --> 00:33:30,020
Prosperity we see today

526
00:33:30,260 --> 00:33:32,580
is hard-earned and can’t be lost.

527
00:33:34,660 --> 00:33:36,740
While Tangut and Khitan are lurking outside

528
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,780
seeking to rob us,

529
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:40,900
more are trying to break us from the inside.

530
00:33:41,620 --> 00:33:44,220
One slip can clobber the state,

531
00:33:44,500 --> 00:33:45,780
leading to downfall.

532
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,620
All loaded, sir.

533
00:33:59,780 --> 00:34:01,580
Are you new here?

534
00:34:02,020 --> 00:34:03,500
You’re fast.

535
00:34:06,341 --> 00:34:08,362
Move the loaded ones. Hurry up!

536
00:34:11,660 --> 00:34:13,300
Looks like southerners.

537
00:34:13,620 --> 00:34:14,980
Nice figure.

538
00:34:15,580 --> 00:34:16,540
If there are a few

539
00:34:16,540 --> 00:34:17,820
good-looking ones,

540
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:19,260
after training them

541
00:34:19,260 --> 00:34:20,380
for a few months,

542
00:34:21,060 --> 00:34:22,980
the returns can grow twentyfold, thirtyfold

543
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:26,140
or even forty or fiftyfold.

544
00:34:26,780 --> 00:34:27,780
Impossible!

545
00:34:29,220 --> 00:34:31,020
Maids doing heavy labor

546
00:34:31,540 --> 00:34:33,340
are worthless,

547
00:34:34,020 --> 00:34:35,580
but for those beautiful

548
00:34:35,900 --> 00:34:37,100
and cultivated ones

549
00:34:37,300 --> 00:34:38,660
who can sing and dance,

550
00:34:38,660 --> 00:34:39,940
rich men

551
00:34:40,100 --> 00:34:41,660
are willing

552
00:34:42,300 --> 00:34:43,380
to pay a fortune.

553
00:34:43,460 --> 00:34:44,448
Be careful.

554
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:47,020
I’m off.

555
00:35:04,100 --> 00:35:05,220
Sir, boat ride?

556
00:35:06,580 --> 00:35:07,900
I’m looking for someone for work.

557
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,060
Who is it?

558
00:35:10,140 --> 00:35:11,660
Our boss Ms. He is inside.

559
00:35:11,660 --> 00:35:12,460
Yuansheng.

560
00:35:15,300 --> 00:35:16,420
I’m here for you.

561
00:35:22,060 --> 00:35:23,620
Huang Dehe deserted out of fear

562
00:35:23,620 --> 00:35:25,460
on the battlefield.

563
00:35:25,740 --> 00:35:27,180
He would be sentenced to death.

564
00:35:28,500 --> 00:35:30,140
Accusing his superior Liu Ping of treason

565
00:35:30,740 --> 00:35:32,620
was the only way

566
00:35:32,780 --> 00:35:33,780
to cover up his crime.

567
00:35:34,620 --> 00:35:36,420
However far he’d go

568
00:35:36,420 --> 00:35:37,580
was nothing to be surprised.

569
00:35:39,340 --> 00:35:40,940
Those at Kaifeng, Hezhong Municipal Governments

570
00:35:41,420 --> 00:35:42,820
and the Provincial Procuratorate

571
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:45,060
tipped him off.

572
00:35:45,620 --> 00:35:47,100
Clerks at Huanqing, Fuyan Provinces

573
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:48,380
and Yan’an,

574
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:50,540
who buried military reports for him,

575
00:35:51,340 --> 00:35:53,940
broke the rules for money.

576
00:35:55,340 --> 00:35:56,300
They thought

577
00:35:56,300 --> 00:35:57,780
they could fool everyone

578
00:35:58,140 --> 00:35:59,140
and confuse right and wrong.

579
00:35:59,860 --> 00:36:01,100
Huang Dehe must’ve had leverage

580
00:36:01,100 --> 00:36:02,380
on them.

581
00:36:02,660 --> 00:36:05,100
Also, they relied on him

582
00:36:05,220 --> 00:36:06,540
to continue to rake in money.

583
00:36:10,380 --> 00:36:13,540
Your Majesty, take the medicine while it’s hot.

584
00:36:31,060 --> 00:36:33,260
Fu Bi handed in a report earlier,

585
00:36:35,340 --> 00:36:36,620
listing all sorts of bribery and corruption,

586
00:36:36,620 --> 00:36:37,940
committed by officials and merchants

587
00:36:38,100 --> 00:36:39,740
either related to Liu Ping’s case

588
00:36:39,740 --> 00:36:40,820
or not,

589
00:36:40,820 --> 00:36:42,820
found in the investigation

590
00:36:43,180 --> 00:36:44,100
of Liu Ping’s case.

591
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:47,940
National safety is at risk,

592
00:36:48,860 --> 00:36:50,740
yet those pests only cared about themselves.

593
00:36:51,940 --> 00:36:52,940
According to my investigation,

594
00:36:53,220 --> 00:36:54,900
a few officials were found

595
00:36:55,260 --> 00:36:56,500
taking bribes

596
00:36:56,500 --> 00:36:57,580
in the form of property

597
00:36:57,660 --> 00:36:59,500
or women transactions,

598
00:36:59,700 --> 00:37:00,740
but they weren’t involved

599
00:37:00,740 --> 00:37:01,900
in this case.

600
00:37:02,100 --> 00:37:03,180
Nor did they know

601
00:37:03,180 --> 00:37:04,380
officials taking bribes

602
00:37:04,380 --> 00:37:05,900
are so brazen!

603
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:08,340
They didn’t know?

604
00:37:11,700 --> 00:37:13,660
They studied hard to pass the exam

605
00:37:14,140 --> 00:37:16,100
and worked their way up to the Capital.

606
00:37:16,100 --> 00:37:17,420
And those scholars, too,

607
00:37:18,180 --> 00:37:19,980
were they not sure about Liu Ping’s treason,

608
00:37:20,260 --> 00:37:21,460
how could they not know

609
00:37:22,180 --> 00:37:23,980
why others bought them houses

610
00:37:23,980 --> 00:37:25,940
and women against the laws?

611
00:37:26,140 --> 00:37:26,980
Why would they

612
00:37:26,980 --> 00:37:28,180
be so generous to them

613
00:37:28,180 --> 00:37:29,420
and offer them so much?

614
00:37:30,060 --> 00:37:30,860
Madam Zhang,

615
00:37:30,980 --> 00:37:32,420
His Majesty is busy with state affairs.

616
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:33,260
You can’t go inside.

617
00:37:33,260 --> 00:37:34,660
He’s with Zhang Maoze there.

618
00:37:34,780 --> 00:37:35,860
What state affair does he have?

619
00:37:36,580 --> 00:37:37,660
All of you

620
00:37:37,940 --> 00:37:39,380
are eager to separate His Majesty and me.

621
00:37:40,260 --> 00:37:41,380
Enough of your nonsense!

622
00:37:41,700 --> 00:37:42,780
Don’t fool me!

623
00:37:42,906 --> 00:37:43,700
Madam Zhang.

624
00:37:47,140 --> 00:37:47,900
You may leave.

625
00:37:48,940 --> 00:37:49,620
Yes.

626
00:38:00,320 --> 00:38:01,180
When I woke up,

627
00:38:01,740 --> 00:38:02,780
it was still dark outside.

628
00:38:03,300 --> 00:38:04,580
You had already left.

629
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:07,060
Today is your day off.

630
00:38:07,420 --> 00:38:08,620
Last night, you said

631
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:10,340
you’d have breakfast with me,

632
00:38:10,460 --> 00:38:11,340
so I

633
00:38:11,340 --> 00:38:12,380
came here to see you.

634
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:14,100
I didn’t mean

635
00:38:14,100 --> 00:38:14,980
to interrupt your business.

636
00:38:16,900 --> 00:38:17,660
Come here.

637
00:38:23,940 --> 00:38:25,180
No one is blaming you.

638
00:38:29,020 --> 00:38:30,620
You look unhappy.

639
00:38:32,220 --> 00:38:34,460
Liaozi, Zhang Maoze

640
00:38:35,220 --> 00:38:36,620
and those maids,

641
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:38,300
they all see me

642
00:38:39,100 --> 00:38:40,140
as if I stirred up trouble

643
00:38:40,140 --> 00:38:41,180
on purpose.

644
00:38:43,060 --> 00:38:43,900
Just now,

645
00:38:43,900 --> 00:38:45,100
I was discussing

646
00:38:45,100 --> 00:38:46,900
important business with Maoze.

647
00:38:47,020 --> 00:38:48,620
Why would Liaozi lie to you?

648
00:38:48,980 --> 00:38:50,140
You’re paranoid.

649
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:51,820
I’m not.

650
00:38:54,060 --> 00:38:56,100
You have no idea how much Empress hates me.

651
00:38:58,140 --> 00:39:00,260
They only follow her orders.

652
00:39:01,140 --> 00:39:02,260
Whatever I tell them to do,

653
00:39:02,380 --> 00:39:03,460
or ask them,

654
00:39:03,580 --> 00:39:04,740
they don’t listen to me.

655
00:39:05,860 --> 00:39:07,100
They only make perfunctory efforts.

656
00:39:09,940 --> 00:39:12,180
I assure you I’m not paranoid.

657
00:39:13,580 --> 00:39:14,740
I’m really...

658
00:39:17,900 --> 00:39:18,820
Once the baby is out,

659
00:39:18,980 --> 00:39:20,180
I’ll be relieved.

660
00:39:20,540 --> 00:39:21,340
The two of us

661
00:39:21,580 --> 00:39:22,980
can keep each other company,

662
00:39:23,580 --> 00:39:25,220
and I won’t bother you again.

663
00:39:34,300 --> 00:39:35,340
What are you talking about?

664
00:39:35,780 --> 00:39:36,860
You aren’t a bother.

665
00:39:37,220 --> 00:39:38,020
Look,

666
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:39,300
had I thought you were,

667
00:39:39,420 --> 00:39:40,580
would I’ve allowed you

668
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:41,740
to rest in my chamber for days?

669
00:39:42,780 --> 00:39:44,660
I didn’t forget that we were going to

670
00:39:44,660 --> 00:39:46,020
have breakfast together.

671
00:39:46,420 --> 00:39:47,340
I even had them

672
00:39:47,460 --> 00:39:49,260
prepare your favorite dishes in advance.

673
00:39:50,140 --> 00:39:51,260
In order to be punctual,

674
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:52,980
I tried to process all my work

675
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:54,380
when you were asleep,

676
00:39:54,740 --> 00:39:56,100
yet you woke up early.

677
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:00,340
Please don’t be mad.

678
00:40:01,300 --> 00:40:02,500
It’s my fault.

679
00:40:02,820 --> 00:40:04,300
I’ll control myself next time.

680
00:40:05,140 --> 00:40:06,220
I’m not mad.

681
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:08,340
It breaks my heart

682
00:40:08,740 --> 00:40:10,020
that you can’t eat

683
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:11,220
or sleep properly.

684
00:40:13,500 --> 00:40:14,740
Breakfast is ready.

685
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:16,220
Once we finish,

686
00:40:16,700 --> 00:40:18,060
I’ll review proposals.

687
00:40:18,140 --> 00:40:20,100
You can stay with me

688
00:40:20,300 --> 00:40:21,260
and have some rest.

689
00:40:24,300 --> 00:40:24,940
By the way,

690
00:40:25,020 --> 00:40:27,100
Empress is going to hold a banquet at the backyard

691
00:40:27,180 --> 00:40:29,940
to treat members of the royal family and others.

692
00:40:30,540 --> 00:40:32,220
They’ll celebrate Huirou’s birthday as well.

693
00:40:33,220 --> 00:40:34,340
She checked with me in advance

694
00:40:34,500 --> 00:40:36,220
if you’re able to attend.

695
00:40:40,220 --> 00:40:40,900
How about this?

696
00:40:41,100 --> 00:40:42,580
Later, if you feel good enough,

697
00:40:42,660 --> 00:40:43,860
you can go with me.

698
00:40:47,060 --> 00:40:48,700
Alright. Let’s go and eat.

699
00:41:02,300 --> 00:41:04,340
= Liu Ping’s son, Liu Yisun =

700
00:41:11,900 --> 00:41:12,860
Nothing has been settled

701
00:41:14,340 --> 00:41:15,420
but His Majesty is kind

702
00:41:15,700 --> 00:41:16,700
and Kuanfu is honest.

703
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:18,820
Your grandmother, mother

704
00:41:19,100 --> 00:41:20,740
and other family members didn’t suffer too much.

705
00:41:25,540 --> 00:41:26,220
Later on,

706
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:29,660
collateral evidence was found against Huang Dehe.

707
00:41:30,340 --> 00:41:31,340
I submitted three reports to His Majesty.

708
00:41:31,620 --> 00:41:32,940
Based on the ultimate result

709
00:41:33,500 --> 00:41:34,260
and reports

710
00:41:34,260 --> 00:41:35,260
sent by others,

711
00:41:36,220 --> 00:41:37,180
accusing your father

712
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:38,500
of leading the troops

713
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:39,860
into Yuanhao’s trap on purpose

714
00:41:40,060 --> 00:41:41,140
isn’t fair.

715
00:41:41,380 --> 00:41:43,500
Huang Dehe tried to exonerate himself.

716
00:41:44,620 --> 00:41:46,460
Hadn’t he quit

717
00:41:46,500 --> 00:41:47,340
out of fear,

718
00:41:47,740 --> 00:41:49,340
leaving a loophole at our back,

719
00:41:49,340 --> 00:41:50,620
we would’ve had a chance

720
00:41:50,620 --> 00:41:51,740
to break out of Yuanhao’s besiegement

721
00:41:52,340 --> 00:41:53,660
and arrive in Yan’an early

722
00:41:54,300 --> 00:41:56,700
to flank the Tanguts there.

723
00:41:57,020 --> 00:41:58,660
Even if we couldn’t win,

724
00:41:59,860 --> 00:42:01,540
at least, we wouldn’t have lost

725
00:42:02,220 --> 00:42:04,060
thousands of warriors at Sanchuankou.

726
00:42:06,020 --> 00:42:08,340
That day, I couldn’t stop Huang Dehe,

727
00:42:09,260 --> 00:42:11,340
so I planned to go back

728
00:42:11,860 --> 00:42:13,780
to kill more enemies with my father.

729
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:18,780
Suddenly, I was shot

730
00:42:19,500 --> 00:42:20,500
and fainted.

731
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,540
After I woke up,

732
00:42:28,740 --> 00:42:29,460
I was surrounded

733
00:42:29,460 --> 00:42:31,380
by my men’s bodies.

734
00:42:47,540 --> 00:42:48,540
Please have a look.

735
00:42:49,540 --> 00:42:51,420
We were shot by these arrows.

736
00:42:58,860 --> 00:43:01,900
How...how dare they...

737
00:43:21,370 --> 00:43:24,460
♪ Isolated kite ♪

738
00:43:24,460 --> 00:43:27,550
♪ Left everything behind ♪

739
00:43:27,550 --> 00:43:30,870
♪ Lost soul ♪

740
00:43:30,870 --> 00:43:34,010
♪ Can’t feel cause he can’t love ♪

741
00:43:34,010 --> 00:43:37,130
♪ Fondness is a beam of light ♪

742
00:43:37,130 --> 00:43:40,250
♪ Shines in the dark ♪

743
00:43:40,260 --> 00:43:43,330
♪ That overshines stars ♪

744
00:43:43,340 --> 00:43:50,190
♪ And nourishes all living things ♪

745
00:43:50,930 --> 00:43:53,650
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

746
00:43:53,650 --> 00:43:57,650
♪ I don’t want to remember, but I can’t forget ♪

747
00:43:57,650 --> 00:44:03,690
♪ My hair turns grey too soon
Laughing at me for being so sentimental ♪

748
00:44:03,690 --> 00:44:06,340
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

749
00:44:06,340 --> 00:44:10,290
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

750
00:44:10,290 --> 00:44:16,670
♪ Towards the direction of light ♪

751
00:44:16,670 --> 00:44:22,890
♪ Light it up for the people ♪

752
00:44:22,890 --> 00:44:29,050
♪ Cure the heartless injury ♪

753
00:44:41,330 --> 00:44:44,980
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

754
00:44:44,980 --> 00:44:48,160
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

755
00:44:48,160 --> 00:44:51,310
♪ When and where are we now ♪

756
00:44:51,310 --> 00:44:54,480
♪ I’m left alone, sobbing ♪

757
00:44:54,480 --> 00:44:57,530
♪ I love you so deeply that left
everything behind ♪

758
00:44:57,530 --> 00:44:59,940
♪ Life is always filled
with the sadness of parting ♪

759
00:44:59,940 --> 00:45:03,890
♪ Forget the past and revenge with a smile,
leave all the obsession behind ♪

760
00:45:03,890 --> 00:45:07,120
♪ We look at each other without words ♪

761
00:45:07,120 --> 00:45:09,920
♪ Drinking wine with pent-up sadness and love ♪

762
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:13,350
♪ Those who love more are always
hurt by who love less ♪

763
00:45:13,350 --> 00:45:16,600
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

764
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:19,740
♪ When and where are we now ♪

765
00:45:19,740 --> 00:45:22,940
♪ I’m left alone, sobbing ♪

766
00:45:22,940 --> 00:45:29,180
♪ I love you so deeply that left everything behind ♪

767
00:45:29,180 --> 00:45:33,950
♪ How can I forget ♪
